ody (Holliston Coleman) is said to be mildly autistic but seems loving andresponsive. She also has some interesting skills, like bringing dead doves back to life. Meanwhile, six-year-old children are being kidnapped and murdered around New York. FBI agent (and former seminary student) John Travis (Jimmy Smits) detects evidence of Satanic ritual in the killings. Then Jenna shows up at Maggie’s apartment, rich and famous new husband Eric Stark (Rufus Sewell) in tow. Eric and Jenna want Cody back immediately, kidnapping her when Maggie hesitates to hand her over. It so happens that Eric is the head of the New Dawn, a foundation that theoretically cures runaway teens of drug addiction, but may have darker hidden goals, especially concerning the upcoming &quot;Black Easter.&quot; <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :smokin --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smokin.gif ALT=":smokin"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.blessthechild.com/">www.blessthechild.com/</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>   <br><br><br>    <p>   <i>"This above all: to thine own self be true."</i><br> <i>"Commit yourself today..and save someonetomorrow"</i> <br>                                     </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon2.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub16.ezboard.com/udotzap.showPublicProfile?language=EN>DOTZAP</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://photoasa.com/disk1/1519/22133_Butterfly1.gif height=35 width=35 BORDER=0 HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Angelight</span><br>  Posts: 2313<br> <font color=#6F6F6F>(4/9/01 7:58:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub16.ezboard.com/funexplainedmysteriesfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=56.topic&index=1>